{"tid":2512934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"職工盟擺街站 警稱犯聚驅趕","createTime":"2021-05-02T06:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T06:26:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f405821c044f3432ce1e9148695d8d39d76a1b42","tid":2512934,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210502/775W3SWLQVHFFMAVUQ5JF6G3OA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2F775W3SWLQVHFFMAVUQ5JF6G3OA%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNtTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=4a284079\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2F775W3SWLQVHFFMAVUQ5JF6G3OA%2F&h=bc6d3600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210502/775W3SWLQVHFFMAVUQ5JF6G3OA/</a><br />\n<br />\n職工盟擺街站 警稱犯聚驅趕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hQwRlLk6vnoyg9qkvlhLnQ0q9fA=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VRVJ4YKTIRETRPF3USXG6J5MGM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhQwRlLk6vnoyg9qkvlhLnQ0q9fA%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVRVJ4YKTIRETRPF3USXG6J5MGM.jpg&h=d52c04ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■街站人員舉起被捕民主派人士的照片。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年勞動節沒有五一大遊行，但有十多名區議員及十餘個政治團體拒絕放棄，在全港「遍地開花」，設置逾三十個街站。職工盟總幹事蒙兆達表示，警方以「會威脅到公共安全同公眾秩序」為由拒批五一大遊行，他深感遺憾。其中在葵芳的職工盟、醫管局員工陣線街站，大批警員傍晚以限聚令為藉口封鎖街站及驅趕街站人員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hdUyZ634fohQ9L2eQD4Kylt-pHM=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M3HWLOMSVBD4TPUV2YFPNPFFOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhdUyZ634fohQ9L2eQD4Kylt-pHM%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM3HWLOMSVBD4TPUV2YFPNPFFOY.jpg&h=7008bd43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員拉起橙帶封鎖街站，並要求圍觀市民離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「硬着頭皮走到最前」<br />\n<br />\n職工盟以「亂世掙扎，負重前行」為街站主題，成員亦穿上寫着「第一排」的T恤設置街站。職工盟執委鄧建華指出，在大眾的認知中，他們未必是走到最前的「第一排」的團體，但隨着走得更前的成員及團體相繼入獄、流亡，他們只能硬着頭皮走到最前，帶着覺悟與一眾港人同行。<br />\n<br />\n鄧建華以《一代宗師》的台詞寄語港人，「有燈，就有人」，在香港步入只剩下謊言的新秩序之際，「好多個我哋唔想回憶，未敢忘記嘅日子」將被抹去，選擇掙扎、不去放棄，是留下的人「當守的道，必修的行」。<br />\n<br />\n街站仿照艾未未《透視研究》之作，向途人派發印有舉中指圖像及有「Never Surrender」、「揸緊宗旨，千祈唔好慣」字樣的透明卡片，同時展示「我真係好X憎而（𠵱）家嘅香港，不如一齊留低，重新嚟過」的海報，及不同過往抗爭及遊行的照片。活動開始前約五至十分鐘，已有約七名警員上前抄下街站負責人、職工盟暫代主席黃迺元的個人資料。警方並在活動開始前已準備好攝錄器材，錄下街站情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BoberUIAzsm2Kl0Iaa56IUm7b50=/510x680/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J5TXLJREI5CLHBQUNCSVWNFBYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBoberUIAzsm2Kl0Iaa56IUm7b50%3D%2F510x680%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ5TXLJREI5CLHBQUNCSVWNFBYU.jpg&h=578d8067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■街站派發的透明卡模仿艾未未《透視研究》之作，籲港人「揸緊宗旨」。"},{"pid":"dc623ab8bcf17b79ec6d2f11f092967716a295af","tid":2512934,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"我都拎左卡仔"}]}